        "data": "<p>Liferay Syncでサポートされている設定の詳細は、以下の表を参照してください。</p>\n\n<h2>Sync Mobile</h2>\n\n<h3>IOS&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 697px; float: left;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>Liferay Version</strong></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\"> <strong>Liferay Sync Connector</strong> </font> </span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\"> <strong>iOS Versions</strong> </font> </span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody valign=\"top\">\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP 7.3</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">7.x</font></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">8.x - 13.x</font></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP 7.2</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\">6.x</font> </span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\"> 8.x - 13.x</font></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-si