yg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP 7.3</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">7.x</font></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">4.1 - 10.x</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP 7.2</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\">6.x</font> </span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">4.1 – 10.x</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP 7.1</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\">5.x</font> </span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">4.1 – 10.x</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP 7.0</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\">4.x</font> </span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">4.1 – 10.x</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2>Sync Desktop 3.2+</h2>\n\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 697px; float: left;\">\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>Liferay Version</strong></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\"> <strong>Liferay Sync Connector</strong> </font> </span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\"> <strong>Required Apps</strong> </font> </span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"> <font size=\"2\"> <strong>iOS Versions</strong> </font> </span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody valign=\"top\">\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP 7.3</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\">7.x</font></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Connector to OAuth 1.0a</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows Vista SP2+<br>\n\t\t\tWindows 7<br>\n\t\t\tWindows 8.x<br>\n\t\t\tWindows 10<br>\n\t\t\tMac OS X 10.8 - 10.15</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DXP 7.2</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-alig