ht: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay IP Geocoder<br>\n\t\t\tLiferay Connector to OAuth 1.0a</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows Vista SP2+</span><br>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows 7</span><br>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows 8.x</span><br>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows 10</span><br>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Mac OS X 10.8 - 10.15</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n\t\t\t<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Portal 6.2</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows Vista SP2+</span><br>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows 7</span><br>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows 8.x</span><br>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows 10</span><br>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Mac OS X 10.8 - 10.15</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">*Sync Connector 4.1.2+ requires Liferay DXP 7.0 Fix Pack 33+</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
